Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《超女》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Previously on Supergirl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未婚妻死于前线的战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My fiancé died fighting on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.88,0:00:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到艾丽克斯差点死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I saw Alex almost die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把坠子给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Give me the medallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能翻译这些标记吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Can you translate these markings?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从嘶吼那里得到了一些东西  一个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I got something from Rip Roar. A name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以利用超女达成我的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I can use Supergirl to achieve my ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她相信我们彼此信任  这么做就更简单了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That is easier to do if she believes there is trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉法克回到幻影区了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Malefic's back in the Phantom Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这里  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You like it here, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I like it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不在状态  超女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You're off your game today, Supergirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I could say the same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么心急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.26,0:00:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I need to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:00:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道利维坦什么时候会再来袭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We don't know when Leviathan will strike next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至都不知道是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We don't even know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要找的是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And what are they after?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的这些未知让我感到焦虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All these unknowns make me feel anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我感到焦虑的时候  我就想打东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And when I feel anxious, I want to punch things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面临过未知的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We've faced unknown dangers before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次感觉不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}This feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不好的预感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have a bad feeling about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽克斯让超查部加班调查利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, Alex has the DEO working overtime on Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定不是别的事困扰你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you sure something else isn't bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我告诉莉娜我是超女前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Before I told Lena I was Supergirl,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常害怕她的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was terrified how she would react.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很怕我会毁了我们的友情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was so afraid I was going to ruin the friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不愿意去想这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I still hate thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着威廉失去朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Watching William lose his friend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我有点不是滋味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}hit a little too close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣恩  荣恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}J'onn? J'onn?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.91,0:02:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在可以出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把坠子给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Give me the medallion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有世界上最复杂的安全系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have the most intricate security system in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全了解了利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know all about Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能完全了解利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No one knows all about Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们无法了解利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Leviathan is unknowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.88,0:02:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经重新启动了顶层公寓的安保系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I've reactivated heightened penthouse security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是对的  卢瑟女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You were right as always, Ms. Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利维坦会不惜代价夺回坠子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Leviathan will attempt to retrieve the medallion at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你何必为了毫无价值的东西去惹他们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But why would you provoke them over something of no value?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠子对我来说很有价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It has value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠子对我母亲来说很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The medallion was special to my mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而利维坦想利用它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and the fact that Leviathan wants it makes it useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱克斯推测超人把所有针对他的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lex theorized that Superman kept every weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在了一个特殊的地方  一个堡垒里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that was ever used against him in a special facility, a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他一直没找到  我想莱克斯说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And although he never found it, I think Lex was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为无害计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I think the perfect dispersal device
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的散播器就藏在那里吃灰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}for Project Non Nocere is hidden there, gathering dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而利维坦会帮我找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And Leviathan is gonna help me find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别低估利维坦的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Please don't underestimate the danger of Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该取消L公司在公园举办的活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You should cancel the L-Corp event at the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会去找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They will come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let them come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超女会救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Supergirl will save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)\an8\fs31\t(0,4190,\fs36)\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\bord1.5\blur1\shad0\pos(188.331,157.909)\c&H020202&\3c&H0B0A0A&\t(0,1730,2,\c&H00002F&\3c&H264E71&)}超 女\N{\fsp0\fs14\t(0,4190,\fs17)}第五季 第七集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Tell us exactly what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们说过了  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I already told you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽克斯  你应该去追查利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Alex, you should be tracking Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  还有嘶吼  但布莱尼已经在查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yes, and Rip Roar, but Brainy's on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别转移话题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}so just stop deflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昏倒前  被困在马拉法克的另一个幻象里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Before I fell, I was seized by another vision of Malefic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个  还发生过这种事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}"Another"? You've had more of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在精神攻击时  我感觉到了马拉法克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yesterday. I felt Malefic during the psychic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是我可以感觉到他就在我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's as if I can sense him all around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么会  我们已经把他送去幻影区了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But how? We sent him to the Phantom Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能想到这些闪回\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All I can think is these flashes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我愧疚的症状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}maybe symptoms of my guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:03:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我们别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know we had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是把马拉法克送回幻影区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but to send Malefic back to the Phantom Zone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他过于危险  不能把他控制在地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean, he's too dangerous to be contained here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  我还是觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Even so, I can't help feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又一次冤枉了我弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I've wronged my brother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第三次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}This is the third time
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在我手上被判监禁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}he's been sentenced to confinement by my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你弟弟自己做了决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, your brother made his own decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能因此责怪自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You can't blame yourself for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看来你正在经历某种创伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But it seems like you're going through some sort of trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许凯莉可以帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Maybe Kelly can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她帮不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}She can't provide the help I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会以火星人的方式来解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'll deal with this the Martian way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠子在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Where's the medallion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿不回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I couldn't retrieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.05,0:05:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一项简单的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was a simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对任何一个人来说都很简单  但...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It would have been simple with any other human, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是卢瑟家的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}she is a Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我保护这个星球多久了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Do you know how long that I've been safeguarding this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从开天辟地到现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从我们和小行星一样大的船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And since our ship, as big as an asteroid,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再到消灭了恐龙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}wiped out the dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后人类崛起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Then humanity rose...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为这个星球的祸害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and became a scourge to this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们千百年来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and for eons we have kept
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制着人类的破坏行为  但现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}their destructive behavior at bay, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们正以前所未有的方式在破坏地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They're ravaging the Earth like never before,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我授予了你为我们的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I granted you the privilege
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做贡献的特权  你却失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of serving our cause, and you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的失败  罗摩·可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is it her failure, Rama Khan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你的失败\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Or is it yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以走了  玛戈特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You can go, Margot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在不需要只来软的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Using a carrot instead of a stick is not what we need right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们将其称为玻璃心一代\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, they are known as the "Snowflake generation."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}2010年后成年的一代\N被认为适应能力差  无耐心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思  他们的心易碎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So what does that mean, they melt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我没说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你目标一致\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You and I both share the same goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想要制止那些不尊重这个星球的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of wanting to put a stop to people who disrespect this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来帮忙的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm here to offer my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮什么忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How can you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在不断改变和进化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The world is shifting, evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未有地快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Moving faster than it ever has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须保持领先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We have to remain ahead of the curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的方法已经不适用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The old ways aren't working--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升的海洋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, the rising of oceans
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汹涌的河流成为常态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and the raging of rivers will always work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缓一缓这股冲劲吧  罗摩·可汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Give the brute force a rest, Rama Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来试试我的科技吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let's try my technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的长者把照顾这个星球的任务留给了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Our elder left the caretaking of this planet to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做成一件事就得亲力亲为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You want something done, you have to do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢大家在这么美好的一天来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you all for coming on such a wonderful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很喜欢在这些小路上跑步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Running these trails has always been my favorite way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能清理思绪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to clear my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是什么  -你感觉到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- What was that? - Did you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常重视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It means so much to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L公司可以参与保护这些土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that L-Corp can have a hand in preserving these grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上有我的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You have something that belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What was that?
