Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了自拍文化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank God for selfie culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这一代人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because of this generation's
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都要实时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}constant need to livestream everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们有了袭击你的人的清晰照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we've got a clear image of your attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道我之前见过这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And I knew I had seen that face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记得公元526年的安提俄克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Do you recall Antioch, 526 AD?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}古叙利亚首都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有场地震\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was an earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是现代历史上第八大自然灾害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was the eighth-largest natural disaster in modern history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  很高兴你能回来  莉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Precisely. It's good to have you back, Lena.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话因他而诞生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A myth was born that this man was the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  科学家坚称\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now, of course, scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然灾害并非人为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}insisted that the natural disasters were natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但意外的历史转折说明他们都错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but, in an ironic twist of history, they were wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而散布恐慌的人是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and the fearmongers were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几处可靠信息确认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Several reliable sources place
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出现在历史上多次犯罪现场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}this man at the scene of the crime throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庞贝末日  1887年黄河洪灾  波拉旋风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Pompeii, the Yellow River flood of 1887, the Bhola Cyclone,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还有诺亚时期的洪水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}even as far back as Noah's flood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个御土师都在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}this Earth-Bender has been spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你叫他"御土师"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Excuse me, did you say "Earth-Bender"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然该怎么形容他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How else would you describe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他  他就是能控制土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He... He literally manipulates the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  庞贝末日  诺亚时期的洪水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Wait, Pompeii? Noah's flood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  他有几千岁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean, what is he, thousands of years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  也就是说  他是外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Correct. Which means that he is an alien
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以长生不老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}with powers of longevity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超出我们的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}this civilization has never conceived of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪人们觉得他是神话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No wonder people thought he was a myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了这么多破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}With all this destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的存在仍然是个谜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}his existence is still shrouded in mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然让人相信他根本不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He's managed to convince the world he doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"利维坦"在希伯来《圣经》中出现了六次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The word "Leviathan" occurs six times in the Hebrew Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Never once does it appear
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在历史科学文献中出现过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}in any historical scientific literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们要怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So how are we supposed to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败一个身份隐秘  活了几千年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}fight a highly secretive, thousand-year-old alien
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力又远超我们的外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}with powers that we have no idea how to beat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识一个人  跟外星人斗了一辈子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, I know one person who spent his life fighting aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真的和假想的都有  -你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- both real and imagined. - Your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.38,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他的小武器都在峰脑堡垒里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know most of his minor weapons are in Fort Summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他真正骇人的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but his truly horrendous ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被超人毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}they were all destroyed by Superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱克斯的很多武器都在孤独堡垒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A lot of Lex's weapons are in the Fortress of Solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这堡垒是超人造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, it's... It's a place Superman created.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面放的是能伤害我们的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We keep things there that can harm us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去堡垒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, you just go to the Fortress,
