Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘶吼和这位御土师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}for Rip Roar and this Earth-Bender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.63,0:10:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超女  记住  最强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Supergirl, remember the strongest,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最有力的武器是知识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}most potent weapon is knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把堡垒信息库里找到的东西都发给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So send me whatever you can find from the Fortress database.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好上路了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You ready for a road trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定我跟去没问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you sure me going is a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Of course. Why wouldn't it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  让卢瑟家的人进孤独堡垒吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't know. A Luthor in the Fortress of Solitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  不过你得穿件外套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's gonna be great. But you're gonna need a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常迷茫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I haven't been this lost
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了曼彻斯特·布莱克后就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}since after I killed Manchester Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时来到了我身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You came to me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我找回了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You helped me find myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I need your help now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣恩  儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}J'onn, my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.70,0:10:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  见到你真好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Father. It's good to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am... I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在意识到我的所作所为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know now what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从你的记忆里抹去马拉法克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When I wiped your mind of Malefic...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下了最深重的罪孽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I committed the greatest sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  荣恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, J'onn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我没有做好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was I who failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是减轻了爸爸的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All you did was ease your father's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我让你为难了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I forced your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任都在我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你让我来不是为了这个  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But that's not the reason I'm here, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  我需要你的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Father, I need your counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉法克要伤害我的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Malefic came after my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历史又重演了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and history repeated itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护他们  我只能把他送回幻影地带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}To protect them, I had to send Mal back to the Phantom Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想忘记这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have tried to move on,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我总感觉他在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but it's like I can feel him nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他就在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's because he is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -你弟弟在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- What? - Your brother is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.78,0:11:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在我的思想里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You mean here in my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在城里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean, he's across town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到莉娜受袭击的场景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I went back to the scene of Lena's attack
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集了土壤样本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and collected samples of the soil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也扫描了御土师的地震波特征\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am also scanning for the Earth-Bender's seismic wave signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前没有发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Nothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是御土师吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Earth-Bender?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘶吼  找到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's Rip Roar. We found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被打晕了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Did they take him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后退\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  有没有受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you okay? Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容易受伤的是你  你受伤了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You're the fragile human. Are you harmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but I am furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们放出嘶吼这个鱼饵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They dangled Rip Roar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.22,0:13:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们会上钩  现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}knowing that we would take the bait, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一无所获\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we've got nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有嘶吼的盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We still have Rip Roar's armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上进行检验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We should start studying it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你没事吗  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Are you all right? - Yeah. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你被划了一道大口子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, but you have a nasty cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  完美无缺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}There. Perfect as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹弗斯局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Director Danvers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...太美了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}This is... breathtaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们在地球上的氪星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's our Krypton on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者  入侵者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Intruder! Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检测到卢瑟家族DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Luthor DNA detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启用L协议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}L-Protocol engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"L协议"  别别别别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}"L-Protocol"? No. No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢瑟  立即放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Luthor, relinquish your Kryptonite ring
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的氪石戒指和物质传送门手表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and your transmatter portal watch immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没戴戒指和手表  我不是莱克斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't have a ring or a watch. I'm not Lex!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上交出武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hand over the weapons at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则堡垒将在十秒内进行攻击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}or the Fortress will take offensive action in ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没有带武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}She's unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-十  九  八  -我来解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Ten, nine, eight... - I'll fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-七  六  五  -快点  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- ...seven, six, five... - Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四  三  二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}...four, three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L协议已终止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}L-Protocol terminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Sorry. I had no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人居然会用这种极端手段\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Superman would take such extreme measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不算极端  要是莱克斯知道这地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, if Lex knew about this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定会不顾一切闯进来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}he would do anything or kill anyone to get in here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟莱克斯不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, you are not Lex.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟超人也不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And you are not your cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We're miles beyond those boys
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这对死敌不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}with their sticks and their stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.48,0:14:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉法克在纳欣诺市  他需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Malefic is in National City, and he needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是真的  我爱的人都有危险了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If what you say is true, then everyone I love is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟伤害不了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Your brother cannot harm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He is a prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁的囚犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Of whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就要你自己发现了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That you must discover on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你一定要帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Father, you have to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎么找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How can I find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须做出选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You must make a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你弟弟永远驱逐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Banish your brother once and for all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.43,0:15:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是拯救他的灵魂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}or save his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  想联系到马拉法克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}However, there is only one way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to reach Malefic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个办法需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And it requires you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒着被他夺去生命的风险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}risk your own death by his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱尼给尼娅发短信说你们遇到了爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Brainy texted Nia that you were both involved in an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就冲来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So I rushed over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  你  你不需要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Really, you have... You have nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  别这样  不要哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, no. No, don't do that. Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是哭  我就会哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because if you cry, then I'm gonna cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我很讨厌在工作的时候哭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and you know I really hate crying at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该打给我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You should have called.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I should have, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.19,0:16:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我肯定打给你  我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And next time, I will. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你要干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Wait. What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have to go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才差点被炸飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You were nearly just blown up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有轻微脑震荡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and you have a mild concussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等完全恢复才能回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You can't go back out there until you're 100 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就到中心数据库了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We're almost to the central database.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿堡垒不要再攻击我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Assuming the Fortress doesn't attack me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你刚才救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you for saving me back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该让自己陷入危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I shouldn't have had to,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在千钧一发的救援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but it does seem like dangerous saves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎成了我们的常态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}are sort of our thing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:17:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  以前都是我救你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Of course, it used to be me being the one that's saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下  我以为我在保护一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Imagine, I thought I was protecting my fragile,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}vulnerable friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不记得我们去卡兹尼亚那次  差点坠机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Remember when we went to Kaznia and the jet was crashing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了救我们的命都急疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And I was frantic to try and save us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想先救我的朋友...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}desperate to save my friend before myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不知道我的朋友其实会飞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Little did I know that that friend could actually fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我让你经历了这些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm so sorry I put you through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我觉得很了不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, it was impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在我还没反应过来时救我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}how often you saved me without me realizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是优秀的演员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean, you're an excellent actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你真相之后我觉得很解脱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Telling you the truth was such a relief,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我好开心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I'm so glad that now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们可以坦诚相对  放下过去的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we can be honest with each other and all of that is behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边请\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在开心了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搜索了全球  就是找不到他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No. I've searched the globe. I can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你力量那么大  居然还是输了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}With all your power, you were defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠子也没找到  甚至还跟丢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}you still don't have the medallion, and you lost them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会解决的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I will fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗摩·可汗  我们是盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Rama Khan, we're on the same side.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我帮你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.46,0:18:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的力量多年来维持着情况稳定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Your power has kept things in alignment for ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但时代已经变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but the world has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.01,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类现在被广大的网络连接着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Humans are connected by vast networks,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息以光速在全球范围内传递\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}information flows across the globe at the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的技术就是我们需要的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My technology is a tool we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有办法找到她们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The way to reach them is beyond you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实碰不到她们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They are beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我在地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But if I can't feel the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不到超女和卢瑟家女儿的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of Supergirl or the Luthor girl on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就意味着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在地球的某个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}they're in the one place on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那里没有土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that is not of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多相式量子处理器吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is that a polyphasic quantum processor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理论上已经讨论过很久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They've long been theorized,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我第一次知道这东西真实存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but I had no idea one actually existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫卡拉·佐·艾尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My name is Kara Zor-El.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想查询懂得御土术的古老外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I seek information on ancient Earth-bending aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一符合描述的外星人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The only alien matching that description
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来自氪星的姐妹星球  扎汉普星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}comes from a sister planet of Krypton, Jarhanpur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于多年内战  该星球被毁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The planet was destroyed after years of civil wars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是五名领导者逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but five of its leaders fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一位有着强大的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}One of those leaders has the extraordinary power
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够控制土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to bend the earth to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How do we stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堡垒的军械库里有武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}There are weapons in the Fortress armory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够伤到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that can wound him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是用来虚弱氪星人的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Weapons thought to weaken Kryptonians.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被莱克斯·卢瑟创造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Those created by Lex Luthor,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是莉娜·卢瑟的哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}brother of Lena Luthor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这些信息够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you, that's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得赶紧去军械库\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, we better get to the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的外星人还有更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If there are more of these aliens,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要很大的一把枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we're gonna need a really big gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该提醒布莱尼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We should warn Brainy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好  -你介意我来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Yeah. - Do you mind if I do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没用过量子处理器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I've never interfaced with a quantum processor before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该挺刺激的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It'd be a bit of a thrill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Knock yourself out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.78,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一能够解救你哥哥的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The only chance of saving your brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是完全卸下你的心防\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}is to let down your psychic shield entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的脑海完全向他展开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Open your mind to him like a flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Complete vulnerability.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他能够看到你的记忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Allow him access to your memories
