Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分明显\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.11,0:23:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氢分子与塔纳安原子一致...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hydrogen molecules synonymous with Thanagarian atoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.36,0:23:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊  一切都这么清晰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Good God, it... It's just... It's clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的抑制器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My inhibitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑制程度减弱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm less inhibited.
