Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我说过想要回去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, I know I said that I really wanted to get back to work,
