Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.85,0:24:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.18,0:24:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当尼娅发信息告诉我你受伤时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When Nia texted me that you were hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.98,0:24:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里一沉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}my stomach dropped...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.52,0:24:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我看你有没有发信息给我  结果什么都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I checked my phone for a text, and there was nothing there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.57,0:24:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我设想了最糟糕的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}so I assumed the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.82,0:24:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我经历过最糟糕的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because I've been through the worst,
