Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.29,0:25:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你那么完美  那么兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and you were so wonderful and so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.54,0:25:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我压抑了自己的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And so I pushed past my fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.75,0:25:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说服自己可以撑下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I convinced myself that I can handle it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.72,0:25:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有那么坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I'm not that strong.
