Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.14,0:25:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯莉  你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Kelly, what-- What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.82,0:25:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.03,0:25:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利维坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Leviathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.40,0:25:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我知道他们的位置了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I... I think I have their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须马上出发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We must leave immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.12,0:25:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  快去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Go. Please, go.
