Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.83,0:32:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能感受到枪在我手上的重量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I could feel the weight of it in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.42,0:32:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的每一根神经都在抗拒  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Every fiber in my being rebelled, but I--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀他  但我知道我必须这样做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I didn't want to do it, but I knew I had to
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.87,0:32:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果莱克斯活着  这个世界就不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}because if Lex lived, the world wouldn't be safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.81,0:32:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友们就不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}my friends wouldn't be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.33,0:32:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我逼自己开枪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So I forced myself to pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.23,0:32:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一枪打在了我亲哥哥的胸口上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I shot my own brother in the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.36,0:32:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在临终时说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}His final words to me were...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.69,0:32:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that I was a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.24,0:32:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最好的朋友  我所有的朋友都在骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that my best friend, that every friend I had was lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.34,0:33:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他临终前告诉我你就是超女\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}With his dying breath, he told me that you were Supergirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.55,0:33:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜  你要相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lena, you have to believe me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.62,0:33:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过羞辱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I never meant to humiliate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.56,0:33:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在我来到这座城市时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No. When I came to this city,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.49,0:33:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向自己保证再也不会相信任何人  然后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I promised myself that I would never trust anyone again, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.41,0:33:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就遇见了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}then I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.92,0:33:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用你的热情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You chipped away at my
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.74,0:33:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和诚挚粉碎了我的盔甲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}armor with your warmth and your earnestness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.14,0:33:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我重新相信人类和友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and you convinced me to trust in people and friendship again,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.73,0:33:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不顾自己的判断  相信了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and against my better judgment, I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.01,0:33:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在告诉你我的致命要害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}all the while telling you about my Achilles heel...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.39,0:33:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是背叛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.34,0:33:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你倾诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I confided in you
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.98,0:33:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过去认识的每个人都背叛了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that everyone in my past had betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.49,0:33:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}About how much it hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.12,0:33:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你撒谎  背叛你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to have someone you love
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.95,0:33:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}lie to you and betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一遍又一遍地告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I spelled it out to you over and over again,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你不要辜负我的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}essentially begging you not to violate my trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.36,0:33:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你不要再一次证明我是个傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}begging you not to prove that, once again, I was a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.36,0:33:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不断地向我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You reassured me ad nauseam
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.04,0:34:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远不会骗我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that you would never lie to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.02,0:34:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你永远不会伤害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that you'd never hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.15,0:34:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而一直以来  在我们的友谊中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And all the while, there wasn't a single
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.04,0:34:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没有一个诚实的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}honest momet in our friendship--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.62,0:34:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  那不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No! No, that is not true--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.34,0:34:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我为你  为我们的朋友杀了我哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No! I killed my brother for you, for our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.08,0:34:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不明白你做了什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Don't you understand what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.21,0:34:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你发现我的身份时  为什么不马上来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When you found out, why didn't you come... to me right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.59,0:34:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来解释...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}so I could explain--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.72,0:34:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"解释"吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}"Explain"? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.26,0:34:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你那么恨我  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If you hate me so much, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.22,0:34:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不在普利策奖典礼上揭发我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Why not out me at the Pulitzer party?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么久还假装是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Why pretend to still be my friend this long?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.80,0:34:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想以其人之道还治其人之身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because I wanted you to experience what you did to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.14,0:34:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体会我的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Feel what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.44,0:34:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你的痛苦和愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I understand your pain and your fury and...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.71,0:34:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.60,0:35:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犯了个大错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I made a big mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.50,0:35:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是我人生中最大的错误  但是求你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}maybe the biggest mistake of my life, but please...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.89,0:35:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜  请不要将大清洗带离堡垒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lena, please don't leave the Fortress with Myriad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.54,0:35:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要因为我的错误而做坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Please don't let my mistake push you to do something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.44,0:35:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是个好人  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- You are a good person. - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.13,0:35:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你再也没有资格评判我的品质\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No, you don't ever get to tell me who or what I am again.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.71,0:35:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者  入侵者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Intruder! Intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.42,0:35:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重新编辑了堡垒的防御系统来攻击我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Did you reprogram the Fortress defenses to attack me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.78,0:35:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.65,0:35:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它和我手上的这个小按钮连接起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And I rigged it to answer to this little button I have in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.68,0:35:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀了我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you going to try to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.25,0:35:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  超女  我不会杀你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No. Supergirl, I'm not gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.71,0:35:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是坏人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm not a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.38,0:35:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该把我当成坏人对待\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You shouldn't have treated me like one.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.18,0:36:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来收拾残局的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And now you've come to finish what you started?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.23,0:36:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.39,0:36:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.05,0:36:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你送回幻影区了  弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}send you back to the Phantom Zone, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.01,0:36:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那里度过了一生  哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I spent lifetimes there, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.55,0:36:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无的一生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lifetimes of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.37,0:36:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有空气  没有时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No air, no time,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.81,0:36:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见  闻不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}no sight, no smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.46,0:36:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Nothing but my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.48,0:36:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中止跳动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}suspended mid-beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.81,0:36:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次极度折磨  没有尽头的中止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}An excruciating suspense that never stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.69,0:37:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏住永不能呼出的一口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A breath you can never exhale.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.40,0:37:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你建议我把你送到那里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is that where you suggest I send you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.59,0:37:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意可以的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You can if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.44,0:37:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我把这个带来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I bring this only now as an offering...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.98,0:37:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to show you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.98,0:37:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来到这里  是真心想来...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that I mean it when I say that I have come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.30,0:37:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.59,0:37:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.51,0:37:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mal,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.34,0:37:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望在我们小的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I wish I could've broken
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把你从那个山洞里救出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}you out of that cave when we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.52,0:37:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能有方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Found some way to...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.22,0:37:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你表明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}show you that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.56,0:37:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的弟弟  而且我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}you were my brother and I loved you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.01,0:37:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You didn't love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我感到羞耻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You were ashamed of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.54,0:37:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我藏了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You hid me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.81,0:37:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我像个怪物一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Banished me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.94,0:38:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放逐了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.85,0:38:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们害怕你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We were afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.74,0:38:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都害怕你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We were all afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.39,0:38:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.05,0:38:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们大错特错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And we were so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.19,0:38:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我把你从我们的记忆中抹去时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I destroyed my honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.70,0:38:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毁了我的荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}when I wiped you from our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.66,0:38:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  马拉  我的所作所为是出于爱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But, Mal, what I did, I did for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.49,0:38:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我想起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now that I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.01,0:38:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受这种痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I cannot live with this pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.53,0:38:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And so, brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.02,0:38:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甘愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I beg your forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.48,0:38:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你联结\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}by submitting myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.16,0:38:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求你的原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to the Bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.11,0:38:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看我的内心  弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Look into my mind, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.40,0:38:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么简单吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's that easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.49,0:38:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把自己交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You hand yourself over to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.65,0:39:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很乐意去看  哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I will look... with pleasure, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.85,0:39:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我会立马杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Right before I kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.10,0:39:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意不惜一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm willing to risk everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.15,0:39:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你看到我的真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}in order for you to see my truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.07,0:39:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心  我的灵魂  我的内心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}my heart, my soul, and my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.63,0:39:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.96,0:40:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我...  -不用说  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- I was-- - No, it's... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.36,0:40:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你熬过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You have been through
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.25,0:40:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段难以忍受的经历\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}an unbearable experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.17,0:40:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失去了你的未婚妻  我甚至无法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You lost your fiancee, and I can't even
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象以那种方式失去你爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}begin to imagine losing someone that you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.46,0:40:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.42,0:40:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如此的坚强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You're just so strong
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.21,0:40:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我没能意识到你仍在痛苦中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that I didn't... I didn't realize that you were still suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.45,0:40:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我没能更细心地觉察到这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and I'm really sorry that I wasn't more sensitive to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.78,0:40:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不  别...  -你先  先\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- No, don't-- - Just... Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.43,0:40:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.70,0:40:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你遇见我时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When you met me,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了我的另一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was just half a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.74,0:40:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的伤口还隐隐作痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was still hurting from my own wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.38,0:40:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你  你帮助我愈合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and you... you helped me heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.06,0:41:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从伤口结成伤疤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, from wounds to scars,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.33,0:41:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再化作回忆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to just memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.53,0:41:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我想为你做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's... That's all I want to do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.62,0:41:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮你愈合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey, I want to help you heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.90,0:41:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I want to be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.78,0:41:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克服你的恐惧  一起面对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and face down your fears and do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.58,0:41:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想帮你愈合\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I want to help you heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.39,0:41:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是不可能的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And what if that's not possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.49,0:41:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这有可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, I know that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.04,0:41:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.52,0:41:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你愈合了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because you healed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.14,0:41:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我说你让我有家的感觉时  我是认真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I meant it when I said that you feel like home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.80,0:41:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也让我有家的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You feel like home, too.

